  "prompt": "What is the easiest way to get my transcript from Mahatma Gandhi University, Kottayam?",
  "response": "To get your transcript from Mahatma Gandhi University in Kottayam, you can follow these steps:\n\n1. Online Method:\n- Visit the official university website (www.mgu.edu.in)\n- Look for the \"Student Services\" or \"Academic Records\" section\n- Follow the instructions for transcript request\n\n2. Offline Method:\n- Contact the University Examination Department directly\n- Submit a written request for transcripts\n- Provide necessary documents like:\n  - Completed application form\n  - Proof of graduation\n  - Identity proof\n  - Payment of prescribed fees\n\n3. Required Documents:\n- Copy of degree certificate\n- Copy of mark sheets\n- Passport size photographs\n- Photocopy of ID proof\n\n4. Contact Information:\n- University Examination Department\n- Mahatma Gandhi University\n- Priyadarshini Hills\n- Kottayam, Kerala - 686560\n- Phone: +91-481-2731511\n- Email: registrar@mgu.edu.in\n\n5. Alternative Option:\n- Approach your college's administrative office\n- They can guide you through the transcript request process\n\nTip: Always verify the current process by directly contacting the university or checking their official website.",
